Compiling on Norstore
---------------------

GNU: 
. /usr/share/Modules/init/sh
module unload gcc 
module load gcc/4.7.2
make -f Makefile_cmor2.norstore_gnu

INTEL: 
. /usr/share/Modules/init/sh
module load netcdf.intel/4.4.0 udunits/2.2.17 uuid/1.5.1 
make -f Makefile_cmor2.norstore_intel


Running on Norstore
-------------------

ssh from login node to cruncher.norstore.uio.no. 

GNU: 
. /usr/share/Modules/init/sh
module unload gcc hdf netcdf 
module load gcc/4.7.2

INTEL: 
. /usr/share/Modules/init/sh
module load netcdf.intel/4.4.0 udunits/2.2.17 uuid/1.5.1

